Planned enhancements
====================

   Here are a few things I'm planning on in future versions:

-  Write this program in C or C++ (currently in AMOS).

-  Add a preferences file for certain options (default dir, default  
   settings, etc...).

-  Add the possibility to search records of all subscriptions. (Maybe,   
   BIG maybe!).

-  More sophisticated search routine. (Anyone want to help?).

-  Add @{" suggestions " link suggestions} from users.


  Let me know what you think of these ideas...

@endnode

