           - Increased the number of allowable characters for Title of
             records from 30 to 40.

  1.10     January 30 1994
           - Added AmigaGuide online help.
           - First public release.

@endnode

@node suggestions "Suggestions and Bug Reports"

Suggestions and bug reports
===========================

   If you have any suggestions for this program, please send them to 
me. I'd be happy to know what the users want and try and implement it in 
the program.

   If there are any bugs that occur while your are using the program, 
a WorkBench style requestor should appear and give the error name. 
Please note down this name and describe as best you can how you came 
about getting this error (and your system) before sending it to me.

@endnode
